tweet: Going to work to stare at the walls until someone comes in for lunch.  Breakfast is a waste of time!
Ate too many jellybeans last night. Still feeling the after effects. I want a cookie and there are none made.  Heating up the oven.
Where are all the PEOPLE!  EAT YOU EM'EFERS! EAT!
Lo' and work in the sandwich mines of GA did loom upon the horizon.  Pressing eerily against my neck. Beads of sweat.
